@startuml
title Clean Architecture - Capas y flujo

rectangle "Feature layer\n(feature/*)" as FEAT
rectangle "Domain layer\n(domain/*)" as DOM
rectangle "Data layer\n(data/*)" as DATA
rectangle "Core/shared\n(core/*)" as CORE

FEAT -down-> DOM : usa casos de uso + modelos
DOM -down-> DATA : define contratos/repositorios
DATA -down-> CORE : helpers/base (opcional)
FEAT -down-> CORE : UI base, recursos
DOM -down-> CORE : utilidades comunes

' flujo de datos
DATA -up-> DOM : implementa repositorios
DOM -up-> FEAT : expone UseCases
@enduml
